# Node / Vite
node_modules/
dist/
*.tsbuildinfo

# Rust / Tauri
src-tauri/target/

# Generated icon variants. Only the source icon.png is committed;
# `pnpm tauri icon src-tauri/icons/icon.png` regenerates everything else
# (PNGs, .icns, .ico, Square*/StoreLogo, plus android/ and ios/ sets) at
# build time. Ignore the whole dir except the source, so new generator
# outputs never dirty the tree or get committed as binary blobs.
src-tauri/icons/*
!src-tauri/icons/icon.png

# Tauri build metadata
src-tauri/gen/
